tests/dpdk/perf/2n1l-10ge2p1x710-ethip4-ip4base-l3fwd-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | Test packets are generated by TG on \
tests/dpdk/perf/2n1l-10ge2p1x710-ethip4-ip4base-l3fwd-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | links to DUTs. TG traffic profile contains two L3 flow-groups \
tests/dpdk/perf/2n1l-10ge2p1x710-ethip4-ip4base-l3fwd-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | (flow-group per direction, 253 flows per flow-group) with all packets \
tests/dpdk/perf/2n1l-10ge2p1x710-ethip4-ip4base-l3fwd-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | containing Ethernet header, IPv4 header with IP protocol=61 and static \
tests/dpdk/perf/2n1l-10ge2p1x710-ethip4-ip4base-l3fwd-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | payload. MAC addresses are matching MAC addresses of the TG node \

tests/dpdk/perf/10ge2p1x710-eth-l2xcbase-testpmd-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | (Partial Drop Rate) with non-zero packet loss tolerance (LT) \
tests/dpdk/perf/10ge2p1x710-eth-l2xcbase-testpmd-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | expressed in percentage of packets transmitted. NDR and PDR are \

tests/dpdk/perf/10ge2p1x710-ethip4-ip4base-l3fwd-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | links to DUTs. TG traffic profile contains two L3 flow-groups \
tests/dpdk/perf/10ge2p1x710-ethip4-ip4base-l3fwd-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | (flow-group per direction, 253 flows per flow-group) with all packets \
tests/dpdk/perf/10ge2p1x710-ethip4-ip4base-l3fwd-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | containing Ethernet header, IPv4 header with IP protocol=61 and static \
tests/dpdk/perf/10ge2p1x710-ethip4-ip4base-l3fwd-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | payload. MAC addresses are matching MAC addresses of the TG node \

tests/trex/perf/ip6/1n1l-10ge2p1x710-ethip6-ip6base-tg-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | TG traffic profile contains two L3 flow-groups (flow-group per \

tests/trex/perf/ip6/1n1l-10ge2p1x710-ethip6-ip6base-tg-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | Ethernet header, IPv6 header with static payload. \
tests/trex/perf/ip6/1n1l-10ge2p1x710-ethip6-ip6base-tg-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | MAC addresses are matching MAC addresses of the TG node interfaces.

tests/vpp/perf/l2/10ge2p1x710-eth-l2patch-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | packets containing Ethernet header, IPv4 header with static payload \
tests/vpp/perf/l2/10ge2p1x710-eth-l2patch-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | MAC addresses are matching MAC addresses of the TG node interfaces.

tests/vpp/perf/l2/10ge2p1x710-eth-l2bdbasemaclrn-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | contains two L3 flow-groups (flow-group per direction, 254 flows per \
tests/vpp/perf/l2/10ge2p1x710-eth-l2bdbasemaclrn-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | flow-group) with all packets containing Ethernet header, IPv4 header \
tests/vpp/perf/l2/10ge2p1x710-eth-l2bdbasemaclrn-ndrpdr.robot-| ... | with IP protocol=61 and static payload. MAC addresses are matching MAC \
